人》中表現亮眼，不但成為贏得最多獎金獎品的嘉賓被封做「獎金獵人」，更在節目裏累積獲得超過20000件花之戀壽司而成為「花之戀毀滅者」，在觀眾腦海中留下深刻印象。近日就有日本餐廳以他的名字作店舖招徠，只要名字中含有「洪天明」任何一個字就能獲得免費花之戀，如三字全中則可得到多達1000件壽司，火速引起全城關注。"},{"pid":"55ebfed2dbec2eb7fb56919d6a5a1d24006cb71a","tid":1972032,"uid":313848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T02:07:00.000Z","msg":"點開薑蓉"},{"pid":"28389c7e58c86cd38d82db2eb3580ab2033bf3b8","tid":1972032,"uid":131767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55ebfed2dbec2eb7fb56919d6a5a1d24006cb71a","tid":1972032,"uid":313848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T02:07:00.000Z","msg":"點開薑蓉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T05:15:49.000Z","msg":"識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba03dfb4b5d7d2d0dc0b3d81cba086a1864985e5","tid":1972032,"uid":131767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T15:15:29.000Z","msg":"睇嚟點豉油嘅人多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1095dc02341a667abbfafa58e3f7a09de9e06bf","tid":1972032,"uid":132418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T02:56:06.000Z","msg":"點 <br />\n仲要由上面淋落去"}]}